.TH tr300 1  "tr300 3.7.0" 
.SH NAME
tr300 \- TR\-300 Machine Report \- Cross\-platform system information
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBtr300\fR [\fB\-\-ascii\fR] [\fB\-\-json\fR] [\fB\-\-install\fR] [\fB\-\-uninstall\fR] [\fB\-t\fR|\fB\-\-title\fR] [\fB\-\-no\-color\fR] [\fB\-\-fast\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fB\-V\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
TR\-300 is the successor to TR\-200 Machine Report.
.PP
It displays comprehensive system information including OS, network, CPU, 
memory, disk usage, and session details in a formatted table.
.PP
After installation with \-\-install, you can also use the \*(Aqreport\*(Aq alias.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-ascii\fR
Use ASCII characters instead of Unicode box\-drawing
.TP
\fB\-\-json\fR
Output in JSON format instead of table
.TP
\fB\-\-install\fR
Install tr300 to shell profile (adds \*(Aqreport\*(Aq alias and auto\-run)
.TP
\fB\-\-uninstall\fR
Remove tr300 from shell profile
.TP
\fB\-t\fR, \fB\-\-title\fR \fI<TITLE>\fR
Custom title for the report header
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-color\fR
Disable colored output
.TP
\fB\-\-fast\fR
Fast mode: skip slow platform\-specific collectors for quick auto\-run
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version
.SH VERSION
v3.7.0
